  ### `flatten`

  **Type:** `boolean`

  **Default:** `undefined`

  This directive will remove the alpha channel of the image, reducing filesize. Transparent pixels will be merged with the color set by [`background`](#background).

  **Code example:**
</Markdown>

<CodeBlock
  {...Astro.props}
  values={[
    {
      src: "https://picsum.photos/200/300",
      alt: "A random image",
      flatten: true,
    },
  ]}
/>
